#test train split
set.seed(13)
n=ceiling(0.8*length(scaledData$selling_price))
train.sample=sample(c(1:length(scaledData$selling_price)),n)
train.sample=sort(train.sample)
train_data<- scaledData[train.sample, ]
test_data <- scaledData[-train.sample, ]
#MODEL SELECTION
